  <Strings>
    <Section>Story</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>258520</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_001</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>レスター博士が、
あんな人なんて……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I would have never imagined the renowned Lester would be 
that kind of jerk... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>259184</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_006</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、他にあてがないんだかラ。
さっき自分で言ったじゃない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But we can't rely on anyone else, this won't be the last 
time we have to deal with him. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>259484</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_007</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そう、だけど……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah...you are right, but... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>259916</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_008Z</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おや、&lt;Claus&gt;に客人か？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText/>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>To Do</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>259916</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_009Z</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>浮かない顔だな。
難癖つけられて、
追っ払われたってとこか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>He isn't a very cheerful person. Yet, you shouldn't blame 
him or drive him away like that easily. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>260700</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_010</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>はい、あの……わたしたち、
精霊のことで&lt;Claus&gt;さんに
相談があって……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText/>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>To Do</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261068</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_011</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あんた、誰？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And just who do you think you are? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261432</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_012</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ちょっと、&lt;Dio&gt;、
失礼でしょ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText/>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>To Do</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261860</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_013Z</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>僕はあの男の友人だ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm that guy's friend. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261860</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_014Z</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>こちらこそ、友人が
失礼したね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I should be the one saying you're impolite to my friend. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261860</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_015Z</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……本当は、
あんなヤツじゃないんだが……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...As a matter of fact, he isn't such a bad person most of 
the time... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>3</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>262336</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_016</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>…………？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>262580</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_017Z</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>学会の幹部連中に、目の前で
召喚術の論文を燃やされた
頃からずっとあんな調子だ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>A bunch of guys from the most privileged colleges burnt his 
Summoning thesis in front of everyone. It's no wonder he got furious. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>263244</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_018</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ひどい……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>How could they be so cruel...? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>263384</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_019Z</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>学会の連中は、精霊の存在なんて
眉唾もんだって思ってるからね。
これ見よがしに論文を燃やして……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Those academic hypocrites did so to regard the Summon 
Spirits' existence as scientifically fake. He was the first to see 
his thesis burning... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>263384</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_020Z</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ミラルドが出て行ってからは
もっとひどくなっていった</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Shortly after that Milard left him and he's been getting 
worse since. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>263384</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_021Z</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……僕が同じ仕打ちを受けたら……
我慢できないだろうな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...If I've received the same treatment like him...I'd be 
crushed... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>3</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>263384</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_022Z</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ところで、&lt;Claus&gt;に何を
相談したいんだい？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText/>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>4</BubbleId>
      <Status>To Do</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>263384</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_023Z</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>僕でも力になれることは
ないかな？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's just a guess but... you don't want to search for the 
Spirit's powers, are you? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>5</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>264124</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_024</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>イフリートってヤツの
いる洞窟へ行くんだよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We were going to Efreet-whatever or other-'s cavern. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>264432</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_025Z</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>イフリートだって！！
君たちだけで行くつもりかい？
あそこは迷いやすいし、危険だ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Efreet, you say!? Are you guys truly planning to travel 
there!? It's very easy to lose one's way there! You must proceed 
with utmost care! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>264752</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_026Z</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>じゃあ、これをあげよう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If you insist, you can have this. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>266068</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_027</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ど、どうしてこれを？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Why are you helping us? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>266376</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_028Z</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>君たちみたいな
子どもだけでは危険だろ。
だからさ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I can't just see some children entering a dangerous place 
and not do anything. That's why. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>266376</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_029Z</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>本当は、僕が付いていってあげたい
んだけど……予定があってね……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I could go with you guys instead of just giving that 
but...I have plans already. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>266516</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_030Z</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>水の力を宿しているこの剣なら
イフリートのいる&lt;Red&gt;熱砂の洞窟&lt;White&gt;の
魔物には効果があるはずだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The power of water lies within that sword and is effective 
against the monsters that lurk in Efreet's place, the Cavern of 
Burning Sand. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>266516</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_031Z</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>さて、僕はあいつの顔でも
見てくるよ。じゃあね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Now then, I'll go take a look at &lt;KLA&gt; myself. See you! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>268636</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_033</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、だからって
&lt;Claus&gt;さんのあんな言い方……
ないと、思う……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText/>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>To Do</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>268636</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_034</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>…………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269172</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_035</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>よし、イフリート
連れてこようぜ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>All right! Let's lead the way to Efreet! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269172</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_036</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>精霊連れてったら、レスター博士、
元気づけられっかもしんねー</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If we find that Summon Spirit, I'm sure the renowned Lester 
will be back in top shape! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269656</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_037</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そう、かな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You're....right... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269964</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_038</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どっちにしろ、精霊の力が
必要だったんだしさ、
ついでついで</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We do have to get the Spirit's power at all costs, anyways, 
so this plays fair for us. We'll get to it, no problem! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270260</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_039</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルールル！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kuruururu! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270732</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_040</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうだね……うん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I agree, yeah! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270872</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_041</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Red&gt;熱砂の洞窟&lt;White&gt;の
イフリート、だっけ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Efreet's Cavern of Burning Sand, was it? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>25</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270872</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_042</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>粗暴で丸焦げにしちゃう
って言ってたけド……
気をつけないと……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>He told us pretty harshly that we'd get completely burn... 
please be careful... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>25</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271436</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_043</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>オレらには
『なりきり士』の力が
あんだから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>All's good though, since we have the power of Roleplayer! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>26</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271436</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_040_030_044</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>全然だいじょーぶだって。
行こーぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>There's no problem about that, let's go! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>26</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
